Package: DGVM3D
Type: Package
Title: 3D forest simulation visualization tool
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steinkamp", "Joerg", , "steinkamp.joerg@gmail.com", c("aut", "cre"))
    )
URL: https://github.com/joergsteinkamp/DGVM3D
BugReports: https://github.com/joergsteinkamp/DGVM3D/issues
Description: This is a visualization tool for simulated vegetation structure/
    succession in space and/or time of forest gap models. Those models should
    contain either individual trees or cohorts (e.g. LPJ-GUESS: Smith et al. (2001,
    2014)).
